# Production environment variables for Firebase Hosting
# IMPORTANT: Update VITE_API_BASE_URL with your actual backend URL

# Backend API URL - UPDATE THIS WITH YOUR ACTUAL BACKEND URL
# Options:
# 1. If you have a custom domain with API subdomain: https://api.rapiddocs.io/api/v1
# 2. If using Hostinger VPS directly: https://YOUR_VPS_IP/api/v1
